<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>500 - เกิดข้อผิดพลาด | Server Check</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sarabun:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Sarabun', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e293b 0%, #0f172a 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      color: #fff;
    }
    .error-code {
      font-size: 8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444, #f97316);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
    }
    .card-dark {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
      border-radius: 20px;
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    }
    .stack-trace {
      background: rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      text-align: left;
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      word-break: break-all;
      max-height: 200px;
      overflow-y: auto;
      color: #fca5a5;
      padding: 1rem;
      font-family: monospace;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container text-center px-4">
    <div class="card-dark p-5 mx-auto" style="max-width: 600px;">
      <div class="error-code mb-2">500</div>
      <i class="bi bi-exclamation-triangle-fill fs-1 text-danger mb-3 d-block"></i>
      <h1 class="h3 fw-bold mb-2">เกิดข้อผิดพลาดภายในระบบ</h1>
      <p class="text-white-50 mb-4">ระบบพบปัญหาที่ไม่คาดคิด กรุณาลองใหม่อีกครั้ง หรือติดต่อผู้ดูแลระบบ</p>

      <% if (typeof error !== 'undefined' && error && error.message) { %>
      <div class="mb-4 text-start">
        <p class="text-danger fw-semibold mb-1"><i class="bi bi-bug-fill me-1"></i>รายละเอียดข้อผิดพลาด (Development Only)</p>
        <div class="stack-trace"><%= error.message %><% if (error.stack) { %><br><%= error.stack %><% } %></div>
      </div>
      <% } %>

      <div class="d-flex gap-3 justify-content-center flex-wrap">
        <a href="javascript:history.back()" class="btn btn-outline-light px-4 py-2 rounded-pill">
          <i class="bi bi-arrow-left me-2"></i>ย้อนกลับ
        </a>
        <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-danger px-5 py-2 rounded-pill fw-semibold">
          <i class="bi bi-house-fill me-2"></i>กลับหน้าหลัก
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
